# Docs & Observability

- Update README/usage for new behaviors, env vars, migrations.
- Document assumptions, trade-offs, limitations (succinct).
- Log actionable messages (no secrets); add metrics/traces for critical paths.
- Keep `AGENTS.md` current when structure/workflows change.

